<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/232871-in-what-ways-and-to-what-degree-are-power">in what ways and to what degree are power imbalances between various cultural groups important thematic ideas in the novel?how are stereotypes used and deconstructed? how does Thomas King&#39;s inconvenient Indian enlighten on the understanding of the politics of representation? what factors might affect the reading of the ending of the novel as hopeful or tragic?</a>
</div>
