        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2926377752" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer3793029854822295576">This is a history book and a biting one. King gives us an overview of Canadian and American native people&apos;s history with governments, broken promises and the way they were always ignored what was theirs.</span>
  <span id="freeText3793029854822295576" style="display:none">This is a history book and a biting one. King gives us an overview of Canadian and American native people's history with governments, broken promises and the way they were always ignored what was theirs.</span>
  <a data-text-id="3793029854822295576" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
